 Roatch）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Papa-Roach.-Credit-Bryson-Roatch.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Papa-Roach.-Credit-Bryson-Roatch-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Papa-Roach.-Credit-Bryson-Roatch-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Papa-Roach.-Credit-Bryson-Roatch-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Papa-Roach.-Credit-Bryson-Roatch-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Papa-Roach.-Credit-Bryson-Roatch-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Papa-Roach">帕帕·罗奇（Papa Roach）</a>在大规模售罄的伦敦表演之前向平静的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/lets-talk-mental-health">心理健康</a>慈善机构提供了20,000英镑的支票。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/papa-roach-interview-nu-metal-new-music-bring-me-the-horizon-mental-health-tour-album-3834201#">爸爸罗奇谈论心理健康，给我带来地平线，并为他们的下一张专辑“推动界限”</a></strong></li></ul><p> NU金属的先驱者向预防自杀的慈善慈善活动介绍了反对生活的自杀慈善活动（冷静），然后最近在伦敦的温布利竞技场售罄的演出。乐队从“蟑螂崛起”之旅的每张门票中捐赠了1英镑，其中包括整个欧洲，英国和北美的停靠站。</p><p>帕帕·罗奇（Papa Roach）主持人雅各比·沙迪克斯（Jacoby Shaddix）在新闻稿中说：“蟑螂崛起的开球令人难以置信。” “平静，以及每个巡回演出中的每个观众，现在是我们为可能需要帮助的人&#39;留下来&#39;&#39;&#39;介绍&#39;的一部分。” </p><figure id="attachment_3837132" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837132" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837132" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cheque-Presentation-to-CALM-7th-Feb-2025.-Credit-Bryson-Roatch.jpg" alt="查看2025年2月7日冷静的演示文稿。图片来源：布赖森·罗奇（Bryson Roatch）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cheque-Presentation-to-CALM-7th-Feb-2025.-Credit-Bryson-Roatch.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cheque-Presentation-to-CALM-7th-Feb-2025.-Credit-Bryson-Roatch-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-